CodeDef lspace2nbsp Filter
CodeDef lspace2nbsp Description Leading SPACE to nbsp
CodeDef lspace2nbsp Routine <<EOR
sub {
        my $str = shift;
        $str =~ s/^( +)/'&nbsp;' x length($1)/emg;
        return $str;
}
EOR

